{"tid":1331474,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"撕便利貼兼毆打兩男 的哥獲准5000元保釋","createTime":"2019-07-19T03:00:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-19T05:54:43.000Z","uid":264614,"like":35,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"5cf2dba897f810ba6953b287fcc3422e158a7467","tid":1331474,"uid":264614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T03:00:56.000Z","msg":"[頭條日報] 【連儂牆】撕便利貼兼毆打兩男 的哥獲准5000元保釋<br />\n<br />\n本月11日凌晨牛頭角淘大花園對開橋底「連儂牆」爆發衝突，一名的士司機涉嫌襲撃2名市民被捕。案件今在觀塘裁判法院提堂，被告今毋須答辯......<br />\n<br />\n連結: <a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1547970/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1547970%2F&d=4e%2FpP7P6HSNE6mjGPWQpDVEyhmTkDJ%2BTCVbHNRNdZc8%3D&h=03ccefa4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1547970%2F&h=0d5a41d0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1547970/</a><br />\n<br />\n5000蚊？我俾夠5萬你 你食我130拳？"},{"pid":"3e1cd6dd57dca9927da083de3ff78799b4470eaf","tid":1331474,"uid":264614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T03:03:34.000Z","msg":"無返屋企咁多日 可能唔認得路啦"},{"pid":"6b5a35e3857bb6802bef9934c30f6b11e49ea3e7","tid":1331474,"uid":264614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T03:03:45.000Z","msg":"有無人幫下佢"},{"pid":"5993d9359e36e55f2579ebcf797751ffce6b4bb2","tid":1331474,"uid":245064,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T03:03:55.000Z","msg":"即時新聞港聞 選擇分類 <br />\n【連儂牆】撕便利貼兼毆打兩男 的哥獲准5000元保釋<br />\n2019-07-19 10:31 文字大小<br />\n 46歲被告黃堅海。<br />\n46歲被告黃堅海。<br />\n本月11日凌晨牛頭角淘大花園對開橋底「連儂牆」爆發衝突，一名的士司機涉嫌襲撃2名市民被捕。案件今在觀塘裁判法院提堂，被告今毋須答辯裁判官批准被告以5000元現金保釋候訊，並須定期去牛頭角警署報到。案件押後至下月30日再訊。<br />\n<br />\n46歲被告黃堅海被控2項襲撃致造成身體傷害罪，於本月11日牛頭角東九龍文化中心地盤外襲撃李真光和麥世傑。<br />\n<br />\n控方申請押後以研究控罪的適合性。控方續指被告與2名事主並不認識，衝突源於附近牆上的紙張。控方又透露，附近有視像片段紀錄紀錄事發經過。<br />\n<br />\n被告今由當值律師代表，透露被告月入約10000元，獨居，獨力供養父母。<br />\n<br />\n法庭記者：蕭文軒<br />\n<br />\n保釋<br />\n未判刑<br />\n因為控方申請押後<br />\n可能想睇下夠唔夠料入佢其他罪"},{"pid":"c69cce98e5963a2d91f0cf71c8ebf93fb7a9fe78","tid":1331474,"uid":199670,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T03:04:52.000Z","msg":"721 港島見 ! !<br />\n「全部同我將push改做721港島見」! ! !<br />\n唔準再推再Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大力文宣宣傳721 plz !"},{"pid":"8ed9461a6e20fede72dff4eda732006abda572f8","tid":1331474,"uid":179967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T03:04:53.000Z","msg":"月入一萬獨居養老豆老母條數點計出黎?"},{"pid":"5a82d2a16e4e6859544a9cf30d8100e468ba6aa4","tid":1331474,"uid":264614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T03:05:12.000Z","msg":"請各九龍灣巴絲 鋪定紅地毯 歡迎佢回歸"},{"pid":"58f2378228ba25204fba29cfee4d5c5a74c144b7","tid":1331474,"uid":264614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8ed9461a6e20fede72dff4eda732006abda572f8","tid":1331474,"uid":179967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T03:04:53.000Z","msg":"月入一萬獨居養老豆老母條數點計出黎?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T03:06:12.000Z","msg":"可能佢係食屎既？"},{"pid":"e95d6de568be90062b6bab33ed3217782f821a55","tid":1331474,"uid":33775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T03:06:51.000Z","msg":"唔係問人有冇洗過碗咩<br />\n而家洗碗冇15k有人做?<br />\n佢做義工架?"},{"pid":"672b1771aa9d8d7dd2c99160d2ecf8241796b25c","tid":1331474,"uid":117894,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"58f2378228ba25204fba29cfee4d5c5a74c144b7","tid":1331474,"uid":264614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8ed9461a6e20fede72dff4eda732006abda572f8","tid":1331474,"uid":179967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T03:04:53.000Z","msg":"月入一萬獨居養老豆老母條數點計出黎?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T03:06:12.000Z","msg":"可能佢係食屎既？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T03:09:45.000Z","msg":"的士佬你都信<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d45eae99ce7def0894a2ad1c967a547749b8cda3","ti